Chrome webstore version of the popular game, The Rubik's Cube!

A fun game that plays in a popup

This chrome extension allows you to play your favorite arcade game, anytime, anywhere! Just click on the Rubik's cube icon in the top right corner of your browser, and start playing! If you loved the rubik's cube, you'll love this game.
